    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving power plant is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback, while the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering remains sharp. Finished in a classic colorway, this chassis offers a balanced center of gravity and the visceral mechanical engagement that defines the M-division's golden era.",
