    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for 2013 BMW M3 Coupe in Carbon Black Metallic. This vehicle features the legendary high-revving S65 V8 engine, paired with a crisp 7-speed DCT transmission. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its history on the open road. Inside, the Novillo black leather seats are supple and well-bolstered, showing only light entry wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound; recent service includes a fresh oil change and a thorough multi-point inspection. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide confident, firm stopping power. This is a driver's car that has been respected and garaged, perfect for someone looking for a high-performance icon that is ready for the weekend or the daily commute.",
